## Troubleshooting

### "Go command not found"
```bash
# Install Go
brew install go

# Or download from https://go.dev/dl/
```

### "Build failed: go.mod version"
```bash
# Update Go to 1.24+
brew upgrade go

# Or download latest from https://go.dev/dl/
```

### "Authentication failed"
```bash
# Clear cached credentials
rm -rf ~/.mcp-publisher/

# Try login again
./bin/mcp-publisher login github
```

### "Domain verification failed"
```bash
# Check DNS record
dig _mcp.aaos2.xyz TXT

# If not propagated, wait 15 minutes and try again
./bin/mcp-publisher publish ../mcp_server_cfo_agent.json
```

### "Schema validation error"
```bash
# Check the error message for specific issues
./bin/mcp-publisher validate ../mcp_server_cfo_agent.json

# Common issues:
# - Missing required fields
# - Invalid URL format
# - Incorrect pricing format
```

